          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφ-ίστημι</span></b> , perf. 3 pl.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφέστᾱσι</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφεστάμεν</span>(<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">αι</span>), part. gen.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφεσταότος</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφεστήκει</span>, 3 pl. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐφέστασαν</span>, aor. 2 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπέστη</span>,
